HEADWORD: Multicostate
<hw>Mul`ti*cos"tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Multi-</ets> + <ets>costate</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having
numerous ribs, or costae, as the leaf of a plant, or as certain shells
and corals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Multicuspid</ent>⟦br⟧
